ews/?id=21865 |script-title=th:\u0e40\u0e1b\u0e34\u0e14\u0e27\u0e32\u0e23\u0e4c\u0e1b\u0e27\u0e19\u0e44\u0e1b !! \u0e15\u0e35\u0e4b\u0e2b\u0e25\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e42\u0e2d\u0e1b\u0e1b\u0e49\u0e32 \"\u0e21\u0e35\u0e19 \u0e1e\u0e35\u0e23\u0e27\u0e34\u0e0a\u0e0d\u0e4c\" \u0e08\u0e32\u0e01 \"\u0e1a\u0e31\u0e07\u0e40\u0e2d\u0e34\u0e0d\u0e23\u0e31\u0e01\"|publisher=NEW18|date=11 October 2018|accessdate=|language=th}}</ref> He is best known for his role as Tin in the 2018 Thai television drama [[Love by Chance (Thai TV series)|''Love by Chance''.]]<ref name=\"a\">{{cite web|url=https://www.saostar.vn/love-wins/mean-phiravich-ngon-den-tu-make-it-right-den-con-loc-lua-love-by-chance-can-quet-dong-nam-a-3941117.html|title=Mean Phiravich, ng\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e8n t\u1eeb Make it Right \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1n l\u1ed1c l\u1eeda Love by Chance c\u00e0n qu\u00e9t \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1.|publisher=Saostar|date=27 October 2018|accessdate=|languagge=Vietnamese}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.dek-d.com/meet/41494/ |script-title=th:\u0e2b\u0e25\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e40\u0e23\u0e35\u0e22\u0e01\u0e44\u0e25\u0e04\u0e4c! \u201c\u0e19\u0e49\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e21\u0e35\u0e19\u201d \u0e14\u0e35\u0e01\u0e23\u0e35\u0e19\u0e31\u0e01\u0e41\u0e2a\u0e14\u0e07\u0e2b\u0e19\u0e49\u0e32\u0e43\u0e2b\u0e21\u0e48\u0e02\u0e27\u0e31\u0e0d\u0e43\u0e08\u0e2a\u0e32\u0e27\u0e46|publisher=Dek-D.com|date=3 August 2018|accessdate=|language=th}}</ref>\n\n==Early life and education==\nPhiravich was born on 5 March 1998 in [[Chachoengsao]], Thailand. He was once the president of the youth in his hometown, Chachoengsao. At the time of its management, its members were only 20-30 members. He graduated Faculty of journalism and Mass communication from [[Thammasat University]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://campus.campus-star.com/star/62696.html |script-title=th:\u0e04\u0e19\u0e19\u0e35\u0e49\u0e44\u0e07 \u0e21\u0e35\u0e19 \u0e1e\u0e35\u0e23\u0e27\u0e34\u0e0a\u0e0d\u0e4c \u0e15\u0e31\u0e27\u0e41\u0e17\u0e19 \u0e21\u0e18. \u0e1c\u0e39\u0e49\u0e16\u0e37\u0e2d\u0e18\u0e07\u0e43\u0e19\u0e07\u0e32\u0e19\u0e1f\u0e38\u0e15\u0e1a\u0e2d\u0e25\u0e1b\u0e23\u0e30\u0e40\u0e1e\u0e13\u0e35\u0e08\u0e38\u0e2c\u0e32\u0e2f-\u0e21\u0e18. \u0e04\u0e23\u0e31\u0e49\u0e07\u0e17\u0e35\u0e48 72|publisher=Campus Star|date=5 February 2018|accessdate=|language=th}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\nMean made his acting debut with a guest role in the Thai BL series Love Sick: The Series Season 2 (2015) in 2015, a talent-searching and reality TV programme produced by [[Channel 9 MCOT HD|Channel 9]].<ref name=\"a\"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://teen.mthai.com/the_boy/154907.html |script-title=th:\u0e2b\u0e19\u0e38\u0e48\u0e21\u0e07\u0e32\u0e19\u0e14\u0e35\u0e42\u0e2d\u0e1b\u0e1b\u0e49\u0e32! \u0e21\u0e35\u0e19 \u0e1e\u0e35\u0e23\u0e27\u0e34\u0e0a\u0e0d\u0e4c \u0e2b\u0e23\u0e37\u0e2d \u0e40\u0e04\u0e27\u0e19\u0e15\u0e34\u0e19 Touchdown Kiss \u0e27\u0e31\u0e22\u0e23\u0e49\u0e32\u0e22\u0e04\u0e27\u0e49\u0e32\u0e43\u0e08\u0e1e\u0e34\u0e0a\u0e34\u0e15\u0e1d\u0e31\u0e19|publisher=MThai|date=10 August 2018|accessdate=|language=th}}</ref>\n\nIn 2016, he then starred supporting role as Tonson in the Thai drama series I Love The Fat Guy 2 (2016) and [[Make It Right (Thai series)|Make It Right: The Series]] (2016) where he played the role as Champ.<ref name=\"a\"/>\n\nMean rose to fame with his role as Tin in the 2018 Thai BL drama series [[Love by Chance (Thai TV series)|Love by Chance (2018)]] which aired on LINE TV and [[GMM 25]] in August 3, 2018.<ref name=\"a\"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.saostar.vn/love-wins/love-by-chance-ngoai-ae-va-pete-con-co-nhung-cap-doi-dam-my-khac-don-tim-hang-loat-hu-nu-3708020.html|title=Love by Chance - Ngo\u00e0i Ae v\u00e0 Pete c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i \u0111am m\u1ef9 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1n tim h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t h\u1ee7 n\u1eef.|publisher=Saostar|date=25 September 2018|accessdate=|language=vi}}</ref> In November it was announced that Mean was cast in the [[MONO29|Mono29]] movie \"Blood Valentine\" playing a police officer. In July 29, Mean's [[MONO29 |Mono29]] movie, Touchdown Kiss, where he plays as Quentin will be released. <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://twitter.com/MONOThaiSeries/status/1062625764367974400|title=MONO29 THAI SERIES on Twitter|work=Twitter|access-date=2018-11-16|language=en}}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n\n===Movies===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=1 align = \"center\" |2015\n|Water Boyy: The Movie\n|Classmate\n|Guest\n|-\n| rowspan=1 align = \"center\" |2019\n| scope=\"row\" | ''Blood Valentine''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thairath.co.th/entertain/movie/1681583|title=\"\u0e21\u0e35\u0e19\" \u0e0a\u0e27\u0e19\u0e04\u0e2d\u0e2b\u0e19\u0e31\u0e07\u0e44\u0e17\u0e22\u0e25\u0e38\u0e49\u0e19\u0e23\u0e30\u0e17\u0e36\u0e01! Blood Valentine \u0e2a\u0e27\u0e22\u0e23\u0e2b\u0e31\u0e2a\u0e06\u0e48\u0e32|date=2019-10-14|website=www.thairath.co.th|language=th|access-date=2019-11-23}}</ref>\n| Sun\n| Main\n|-\n| align = \"center\" | 2020\n|Pee Nak 2<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gossipstar.com/%e0%b8%ab%e0%b8%99%e0%b8%b1%e0%b8%87/221327.html|title=\u0e21\u0e35\u0e19-\u0e2d\u0e2d\u0e01\u0e31\u0e2a \u0e19\u0e33\u0e17\u0e35\u0e21\u0e1a\u0e27\u0e07\u0e2a\u0e23\u0e27\u0e07\u0e20.\u0e1e\u0e35\u0e48\u0e21\u0e32\u0e012 \u0e01\u0e32\u0e23\u0e31\u0e19\u0e15\u0e35\u0e04\u0e27\u0e32\u0e21\u0e2e\u0e32\u0e44\u0e21\u0e48\u0e41\u0e1e\u0e49\u0e20\u0e32\u0e04\u0e41\u0e23\u0e01|last=\u0e01\u0e30\u0e17\u0e34|date=2019-10-04|website=GossipStar|access-date=2019-11-23}}</ref>\n|Tho ( min-jun\n|Main\n|}\n\n===Television series===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n! scope=\"col\" | Year\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=1 align = \"center\" |2015\n| scope=\"row\" | ''Love Sick: The Series Season 2'' \n| Student\n| Guest\n|-\n| rowspan=2 align = \"c