ne.com/board/view.php?sid=4350337|title=5 \u0e2b\u0e19\u0e38\u0e48\u0e21 Kissboys TH \u0e01\u0e31\u0e1a\u0e04\u0e2d\u0e19\u0e40\u0e2a\u0e34\u0e23\u0e4c\u0e15\u0e1b\u0e34\u0e14\u0e42\u0e1b\u0e23\u0e40\u0e08\u0e04\u0e17\u0e35\u0e48\u0e40\u0e15\u0e47\u0e21\u0e44\u0e1b\u0e14\u0e49\u0e27\u0e22\u0e04\u0e27\u0e32\u0e21\u0e17\u0e23\u0e07\u0e08\u0e33\u0e41\u0e2a\u0e19\u0e1e\u0e34\u0e40\u0e28\u0e29|website=SIAMZONE.COM|access-date=2019-11-09}}</ref>\n|KBank Siam Pic-Ganesha Theatre\n|8 September 2019\n|}\n\n== Variety shows ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n! scope=\"col\" |Year\n! scope=\"col\" |Title\n! scope=\"col\" |Type\n! scope=\"col\" |Network\n! scope=\"col\" |Air time\n|-\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" |2019\n|Kissboys Thailand<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.komchadluek.net/news/ent/374870|title='KissBoys TH' \u0e41\u0e16\u0e25\u0e07\u0e04\u0e27\u0e32\u0e21\u0e1b\u0e31\u0e07\u0e01\u0e31\u0e1a\u0e20\u0e32\u0e23\u0e01\u0e34\u0e08\u0e1e\u0e34\u0e0a\u0e34\u0e15\u0e43\u0e08\u0e17\u0e35\u0e48\u0e0d\u0e35\u0e48\u0e1b\u0e38\u0e48\u0e19|date=2019-06-09|website=www.komchadluek.net|language=TH|access-date=2019-11-09}}</ref>\n|Reality Show\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" |[[MCOT HD|9 MCOT HD]]\n[https://www.facebook.com/kissboysth FB Kissboys TH]\n|13 July 2019 \u2013 7 September 2019\n|}\n\n==References==\n\n<references />\n\n== External links ==\n\n* {{Instagram|m34nismind}}\n* {{IMDb name|8528876}}\n\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Attachitsataporn, Phiravich}}\n[[Category:1998 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Male actors from Bangkok|Phiravich Attachitsataporn]]\n[[Category:Thai male film actors|Phiravich Attachitsataporn]]\n[[Category:Thai male television actors|Phiravich Attachitsataporn]]\n[[Category:21st-century Thai male actors|Phiravich Attachitsataporn]]\n[[Category:Thai people of Chinese descent]]\n[[Category:Thammasat University alumni]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox person\n| name         = Phiravich Attachitsataporn\n| image        = Phiravich 