7-hiu/|title=\u0e43\u0e04\u0e23\u0e21\u0e35\u0e41\u0e1f\u0e19\u0e2d\u0e2d\u0e01\u0e08\u0e32\u0e01\u0e41\u0e01\u0e4a\u0e07\u0e40\u0e23\u0e32\u0e44\u0e1b [BYE] \u2013 Jiggaban|last=jiggaban|language=en-US|access-date=2019-11-23}}</ref>\n|BYE\n|Hi-U\n|}\n\n== Discography ==\n\n=== Songs ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n! scope=\"col\" |Year\n! scope=\"col\" |Song Title\n! scope=\"col\" |English Title\n! scope=\"col\" |Note\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align: center;\" |2019\n|\u0e40\u0e1e\u0e34\u0e48\u0e07\u0e44\u0e14\u0e49\u0e23\u0e39\u0e49<ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.thairath.co.th/entertain/news/1613770|title=\u201c\u0e04\u0e34\u0e2a\u0e1a\u0e2d\u0e22 \u0e44\u0e17\u0e22\u0e41\u0e25\u0e19\u0e14\u0e4c\u201d \u0e43\u0e0a\u0e49\u0e0a\u0e35\u0e27\u0e34\u0e15\u0e40\u0e23\u0e35\u0e22\u0e25\u0e25\u0e34\u0e15\u0e35\u0e49\u0e2a\u0e38\u0e14\u0e1f\u0e34\u0e19!|date=2019-07-13|website=www.thairath.co.th|language=th|access-date=2019-11-09}}</ref>\n|Just know\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Kissboys TH single\n|-\n|\u0e14\u0e35\u0e15\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e43\u0e08<ref name=\":0\" />\n|Good to heart\n|}\n\n== Live shows ==\n\n=== Stage play ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n! scope=\"col\" |Year\n! scope=\"col\" |Title\n! scope=\"col\" |Role\n! scope=\"col\" |Place\n! scope=\"col\" |Date\n|-\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" |2019\n|Who is the real murderer?\n|Phum\n|Art Center @Thailand. Prof. Dr.Saroj Buasri Innovation Building, Srinakharinwirot University\n|8 June 2019\n|}\n\n=== Concert ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n! scope=\"col\" |Year\n! scope=\"col\" |Title\n! scope=\"col\" |Place\n! scope=\"col\" |Date\n|-\n| style=\"text-align: center;\" |2019\n|Kissboys TH The Final Concert<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.siamzone.com/board/view.php?sid=4350337|title=5 \u0e2b\u0e19\u0e38\u0e48\u0e21 Kissboys TH \u0e01\u0e31\u0e1a\u0e04\u0e2d\u0e19\u0e40\u0e2a\u0e34\u0e23\u0e4c\u0e15\u0e1b\u0e34\u0e14\u0e42\u0e1b\u0e23\u0e40\u0