uent Unplugged tour in Jan and Feb 2018. He also Played keyboards for their \"Electric Summer\" Tour in June through August 2018.\n\n==Honors==\n*2004: \u00abJazzIntro\u00bb Award with the band ''In the Country'' at the [[Moldejazz]]<ref>{{cite web\n| url = http://www.moldejazz.no/2010/index.php?page_id=12883\n| title = JazzIntro prisen\n| publisher = [[Moldejazz]]\n| accessdate = 2011-05-05\n| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304063048/http://www.moldejazz.no/2010/index.php?page_id=12883\n| archive-date = 2016-03-04\n| url-status = dead\n}}</ref>\n*2004: [[Spellemannprisen]] in the class jazz with [[Solveig Slettahjell]] and pop music with [[The National Bank (band)|The National Bank]]<ref name=snl>{{cite web |url=http://snl.no/Morten_Qvenild |title=Morten Qvenild Biography |language=Norwegian |last=Hammer\u00f8 |first=Tor |publisher=[[Store Norske Leksikon]] |date=2009-02-14 |accessdate=2014-04-14}}</ref>\n*2007: [[Kongsberg Jazz Award]]<ref>{{cite web\n| url = http://www.ballade.no/nmi.nsf/doc/art2007070715191787085374\n| title = Musikerprisen til Morten Qvenild\n| publisher = Norsk Musikkinformasjon\n| date = 2007-07-07\n| accessdate = 2011-05-05\n| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071123062208/http://www.ballade.no/nmi.nsf/doc/art2007070715191787085374\n| archive-date = 2007-11-23\n| url-status = dead\n}}</ref>\n*2016: [[Edvardprisen]] in the open class for the album ''Personal Piano''\n\n==Discography==\n{{main|Morten Qvenild Discography}}\n\n=== Solo albums ===\n*[[2015 in music|2015]]: ''Personal Piano'' ([[list of Hubro albums|Hubro Music]])\n*[[2016 in music|2016]]: ''The HyPer(Sonal) Piano Project - Towards A (Per)Sonal Topography Of Grand Piano And Electronics'' (Hubro Music)\n\n=== Collaborations ===\n;[[In The Country]]\n*[[2005 in music|2005]]: ''This Was the Pace of My Heartbeat'' ([[Rune Grammofon]])<ref name=snl/>\n*[[2006 in music|2006]]: ''Losing Stones, Collecting Bones'' (Rune Grammofon)\n*[[2009 in music|2009]]: ''Whit